      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPEEDY ZIPPER (3) scored his maiden success two back then hit the frame last time when second and beaten a neck at Maitland over 450m (25.22). In form and looks a top chance again. HUNTERVIEW JACK (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at The Gardens behind Turn Up Ace (23.01) in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from five starts. Can feature again. FUGENZO (2) resumed in a Grade 5 at this track and ran into the frame when second over 388m (22.26). Fitter and longer journey looks ideal. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. PARISIAN JET (8) will be hard to beat despite making his debut at this trip.",
